     H            Y.
     F** UEXR05E *******************************************
     F*  EXSUB - GET LOCATION OF AKBPP01 FROM SHIN/DATE    *
     F*  J. WATANABE  2024.06.19                           *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR05E'
     F*                    PARM           P@SHN  12
     F*                    PARM           P@DPT   4
     F*                    PARM           P@DAT   8
     F*                    PARM           O@LOC   6
     F*                    PARM           O@SET   5
     F*                    PARM           O@LT    3
     F*  IN  P@SHN  12   IAF PART#
     F*  "   P@DPT   4   DEPT
     F*  "   P@DAT   8   DATE   (BLANK=TODAY)
     F*  OUT O@LOC   6   LOCATION
     F*  "   O@SET   5   MAX SET#
     F*  "   O@LT    3   LEAD TIME
      ******************************************************
     FAKBPL07 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 K1SHIN
     I                                        1   5 K1SHN1
     I                                        6  10 K1SHN2
     I                                       11  12 K1SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 L1TKR
     I                                        1   1 L1TKR1
     I                                        2   3 L1TKR2
     I                                        4   5 L1TKR3
     I                                        6   6 L1TKR4
      ******************************************************
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      ******************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@SHN  12
     C                     PARM           P@DPT   4
     C                     PARM           P@DAT   8
     C                     PARM           O@LOC   6
     C                     PARM           O@SET   5
     C                     PARM           O@LT    3
      *
     C           K#07      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K1SHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           K1SHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           K1SHN3  2
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    O@LOC
     C                     MOVE '00000'   O@SET
     C                     MOVE '000'     O@LT
     C                     MOVELP@SHN     K1SHIN
     C                     MOVELP@DPT     @DPT    40
     C                     MOVELP@DAT     @DAT    80
      *
     C           K#07      SETLLAKBPL07
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           K#07      READEAKBPL07                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           L1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           L1BMON    ORNE @DPT
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           L1UKHZ    IFGT @DAT
     C           L1STHZ    ORLT @DAT
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELL1TKR     O@LOC
     C                     MOVELL1KMAX    O@SET
     C                     MOVELL1LTIM    O@LT
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
